00:15.182 --> 00:17.901
<i>We're going to a very distant land</i>

00:17.893 --> 00:20.271
<i>With Finn and Jake and Marceline</i>

00:20.270 --> 00:21.988
<i>And Princess Bubblegum</i>

00:22.105 --> 00:24.358
<i>It's Adventure Time</i>

00:33.200 --> 00:35.328
PEPPERMINT BUTLER: <i>"Evil</i> is <i>rising.</i>

00:35.327 --> 00:39.833
<i>"In vile power, the fiend walks
among us again.</i>

00:40.290 --> 00:41.963
<i>"The Vampire King.</i>

00:42.042 --> 00:45.091
<i>"With all my investigations
into the supernatural,</i>

00:45.212 --> 00:48.466
<i>"I should know better, but I can't help it.</i>

00:48.465 --> 00:51.093
<i>"I'm dying to see him in person!"</i>

00:51.218 --> 00:53.721
