01:05.816 --> 01:09.320
- <i>D020.</i>
- <i>Merci</i> and <i>adios.</i>

01:09.403 --> 01:10.450
Wait!

01:10.654 --> 01:12.577
Uh, how's it going?

01:12.823 --> 01:13.949
It's good, you know?

01:14.074 --> 01:16.202
Uh, Marceline's got all her powers back.

01:16.285 --> 01:18.083
She's getting ready to give the Vampire King

01:18.078 --> 01:20.547
a big, fat whompin', uh, I hope.

01:20.789 --> 01:22.462
Um, while that's going down,

01:22.541 --> 01:24.339
do you think you could ask the V.K.

01:24.334 --> 01:25.836
To sign something for me?

01:26.295 --> 01:27.968
That would be weird.

01:28.046 --> 01:29.172
You're weird.

01:30.299 --> 01:31.596
(DOOR SLAMS)

01:31.967 --> 01:36.848
(BUBBLEGUM COUNTING IN GERMAN)

01:37.055 --> 01:38.477
<i>(SINGING) Makin' stake-uhs</i>

01:38.473 --> 01:40.316
<i>Makin' mega-stake-uhs</i>

01:40.434 --> 01:42.732
<i>Take some stake-uhs
and I make a mega-stake-uh</i>

01:42.853 --> 01:45.481
I dreamed about you
while I was in my poison coma.

01:45.689 --> 01:47.487
I was all old and withered,

01:47.482 --> 01:49.985
and you were still nice and pink.

01:49.985 --> 01:53.239
You think I'm nice? Aw, brains, I lost count!

01:53.363 --> 01:55.616
That's okay. I'm done with bat jacks.

01:55.866 --> 01:58.619
(SIGHS) I have this weird feeling in my tums.

01:58.827 --> 02:00.875
'Cause you're scared of the Vampire King?

02:00.996 --> 02:04.842
No, it's not fear. I know what that feels like.

02:05.000 --> 02:07.753
So, maybe it's love?

02:07.836 --> 02:09.554
(STOMACH GURGLING)

02:09.670 --> 02:11.673
Oh! What is it?

02:11.798 --> 02:13.550
(IMITATES TRUMPET BLOWING)

02:13.759 --> 02:17.138
It's the herald of a new snack dawn!

02:19.431 --> 02:21.058
(SNIFFS) Oh, yeah.

02:21.183 --> 02:24.312
- (MUNCHING)
- I arranged a little snacky-snack for the team.

02:24.519 --> 02:26.772
I love you, Bonnibel.

02:27.022 --> 02:31.823
Yeah, me too, Bonnibel. (CRUNCHING)

02:33.779 --> 02:34.826
Oh!

02:35.656 --> 02:36.953
'(GULPS)
'(THUDS)

02:36.948 --> 02:40.828
Holy macaroni! Can we do this all the time?

02:40.952 --> 02:43.330
Later, we can, all the time.

02:43.330 --> 02:45.833
But for now-now,
we got to get our plan together.

02:45.832 --> 02:49.837
(MUNCHING) Easy. First, take down the V.K.,

02:49.920 --> 02:53.595
kill him, destroy him, and...

02:53.674 --> 02:55.176
Kill him! (MUNCHES)

02:55.300 --> 02:58.224
I like this plan! It's got good bones!

02:58.345 --> 03:00.222
Well, the devil's in the details.

03:00.305 --> 03:02.228
Like, how do we even find him?

03:02.224 --> 03:04.852
- (WIND WHISTLING)
- VAMPIRE KING: I come to you.

03:07.854 --> 03:09.481
Vampire King!

03:09.606 --> 03:11.358
In the flesh.

03:11.608 --> 03:14.111
Not for long, sucka!

03:14.361 --> 03:16.739
Whoa! I just want to talk.

03:16.988 --> 03:18.240
Oh, really?

03:18.365 --> 03:20.868
Why don't you step inside for a nice chat?

03:20.992 --> 03:22.084
Ahhh!

03:22.369 --> 03:23.495
No, thank you.

03:23.745 --> 03:25.247
Whoa-oh-oh!

03:25.372 --> 03:26.749
(SCREAMING)

03:28.083 --> 03:29.460
(HISSES)

03:30.210 --> 03:31.462
(MARCELINE GRU NTS)

03:33.004 --> 03:35.006
Just hear me out, Marceline.

03:35.090 --> 03:36.216
Hear this!

03:36.383 --> 03:37.384
(SPLAT)

03:37.592 --> 03:38.639
Yowch!

03:38.844 --> 03:41.017
- Will you calm down and listen to...
- (FINN SCREAMING)

03:41.221 --> 03:42.894
(SCREAMING)

03:42.973 --> 03:44.270
(GRUNTS)

03:44.891 --> 03:46.143
<i>(BREATHES HEAVXLY) ShOOL.</i>

03:46.268 --> 03:47.360
(GROWLS)

03:48.854 --> 03:50.777
- (EXHALES SHARPLY)
- Sorry.

03:50.897 --> 03:52.023
(FINN GROANING)

03:52.149 --> 03:53.867
(GROANING)

03:53.984 --> 03:57.158
Stay calm and nobody gets hurt.

03:57.279 --> 03:58.906
I know what you must think of me,

03:59.114 --> 04:00.286
and you'd be right.

04:00.407 --> 04:03.536
My thirst for blood is an awesome force.

04:03.618 --> 04:06.417
But in these new times,
I have a chance to try...

04:06.413 --> 04:07.665
A different course.

04:08.874 --> 04:09.875
I think I want to...

04:11.752 --> 04:13.254
(SIZZLING)

04:13.545 --> 04:15.047
Roll out! (GRUNTS)

04:15.505 --> 04:16.882
Thorn arm...

04:16.882 --> 04:18.007
Activate!

04:19.760 --> 04:21.387
You gonna help or what?

04:21.595 --> 04:23.643
Let me finish my thought.

04:23.638 --> 04:24.764
Stake you!

04:24.890 --> 04:26.016
Okay, go ahead.

04:26.224 --> 04:28.022
This is the old way.

04:28.018 --> 04:31.022
Agents of darkness and light in a tug-of-war.

04:31.021 --> 04:34.150
But now a creature can step out
of that struggle.

04:34.149 --> 04:38.029
In this age, why would I want to
be the Vampire King anymore?

04:38.028 --> 04:40.030
I don't know. Why would you?

04:40.030 --> 04:41.156
I wouldn't.

04:41.156 --> 04:42.408
I submit.

04:42.532 --> 04:45.285
Remove the vampire essence from my blood.

04:45.410 --> 04:48.289
Free me from the shackles of my station.

04:49.915 --> 04:51.667
Hyah! (GASPS)

04:52.751 --> 04:54.628
Finn, what the heck?

04:54.795 --> 04:56.422
It's against my code to strike a foe

04:56.421 --> 04:58.048
who's raised their bottom to the sky.

04:58.131 --> 05:00.304
The enchiridion explicitly states so.

05:00.425 --> 05:01.927
Demma your rules.

05:02.010 --> 05:03.683
Demma good rule, dough.

05:03.762 --> 05:06.436
- Out of my way!
- (FINN SPUTFERS)

05:06.556 --> 05:07.933
Look, eh?

05:08.183 --> 05:11.938
Look at these babies.
These pleading puppies.

05:12.312 --> 05:13.564
(MARCELINE YELLS)

05:13.647 --> 05:14.694
(MARCELINE GROANS)

05:14.689 --> 05:16.191
Whoops! Should have staked him.

05:16.566 --> 05:17.692
(AIR RUSHING)

05:17.818 --> 05:18.944
(GROANS)

05:20.821 --> 05:23.950
How many times do you
want to do this, Marceline?

05:24.074 --> 05:25.701
Our lives are magnetized.

05:25.826 --> 05:27.453
We're in a negative loop.

05:27.577 --> 05:29.830
But we can change our outcome this time!

05:29.955 --> 05:33.209
I like the outcome where you get staked.

05:33.291 --> 05:35.043
And you become a vampire?

05:35.210 --> 05:37.087
(GRUNTS)

05:37.838 --> 05:39.215
Marceline,

05:39.297 --> 05:42.471
I know I was ruthless in the past, but tell me,

05:42.467 --> 05:45.095
what's the one thing
you've noticed about the world

05:45.220 --> 05:48.190
since you beat me
all those hundreds of years ago?

05:48.306 --> 05:51.230
Everything repeats over and over again.

05:51.309 --> 05:52.982
No one learns anything

05:53.103 --> 05:55.856
because no one lives long enough
to see the pattern, I guess.

05:55.981 --> 05:57.858
But you've lived long enough.

05:57.983 --> 05:59.235
I know, duh.

05:59.359 --> 06:01.612
And you still think this is the right way?

06:01.695 --> 06:02.742
Fighting me?

06:02.988 --> 06:06.242
The other Way's like a black hole.
An unknown.

06:06.241 --> 06:07.834
So, let's consult a witch.

06:11.246 --> 06:12.498
No witches.

06:12.831 --> 06:17.086
(VAMPIRE KING VOCALIZING)

06:17.502 --> 06:20.881
I'm not afraid of the unknown!

06:20.881 --> 06:23.134
(POUNDING)

06:23.258 --> 06:27.263
I have the power to change destiny!

06:27.262 --> 06:28.639
(THUNDER CRASHES)

06:28.722 --> 06:32.727
Queen of vampires.
You weigh the scales of fate.

06:32.976 --> 06:36.025
Spill my guts or face the unknown.

06:36.146 --> 06:38.524
Either way, I will not bite.

06:38.607 --> 06:43.033
For turning you, would subjugate me
to the wheel of fortune,

06:43.153 --> 06:46.783
and I am a king, not a hamster.

06:47.032 --> 06:50.286
My path runs straight into the void

06:50.285 --> 06:54.040
on a sick, flaming chariot!

06:54.122 --> 06:56.796
ALL: Wow!

06:57.042 --> 06:59.170
Stake me! I will not hide.

06:59.169 --> 07:00.295
(THUNDER CRASHES)

07:00.295 --> 07:01.797
Do it, chicken.

07:01.880 --> 07:03.928
You make me sick!

07:04.049 --> 07:05.050
(GRUNTING)

07:06.051 --> 07:07.303
Okay, dag!

07:07.385 --> 07:08.807
MARCELINE: We'll take your stupid thing out.

07:08.803 --> 07:09.929
My What?

07:10.013 --> 07:12.061
Your dang vamp juice, come on!

07:12.641 --> 07:13.688
Cool.

07:14.142 --> 07:16.520
(GRUNTING)

07:16.895 --> 07:17.942
(SIGHS)

07:18.146 --> 07:19.193
FINN: Let 'er rip!

07:19.189 --> 07:20.190
- BUBBLEGUM: Wait!
- Huh?

07:20.315 --> 07:21.407
Ahhh!

07:21.524 --> 07:22.571
JAKE: Whoops!

07:23.443 --> 07:24.569
Truce, you GUYS-

07:24.819 --> 07:26.321
No funny business.

07:26.446 --> 07:28.824
