07:34.079 --> 07:35.706
(FINN SCREAMING)

07:35.830 --> 07:36.831
Oof!

07:36.915 --> 07:38.212
Finish him!

07:38.208 --> 07:39.960
Bam, bam, bam, bam, bam, bam,
bam, bam, bam!

07:39.960 --> 07:41.212
Finn, you can stop.

07:41.294 --> 07:42.466
Oh, okay, now we're stopping.

07:42.587 --> 07:43.588
Sorry, dude.

07:43.588 --> 07:44.840
It's chill.

07:45.298 --> 07:47.096
See? No funny business.

07:47.968 --> 07:49.595
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)

07:51.596 --> 07:53.815
- Hey, Jake?
- What?

07:55.183 --> 07:57.356
(POPS)

