08:40.437 --> 08:41.563
BUBBLEGUM: Is the lab ready?

08:41.645 --> 08:45.196
Of course. (FRIGHTFULLY) Is he here?

08:45.316 --> 08:46.442
(GASPS)

08:47.068 --> 08:48.194
